text: Onnia is a genus of fungi in the family Hymenochaetaceae. The widely distributed genus contains five species. ==Species list== *Onnia circinata *Onnia incisa *Onnia musashiensis *Onnia orientalis *Onnia scaura *Onnia tomentosa ==References== ==External links== Category:Hymenochaetaceae Category:Agaricomycetes genera
title: Onnia (fungus)
